name: teal / grey mama wrap
description:
why not treat yourself or someone you love to perfect comfort at this blossoming time....

wrap & tie style maternity & breastfeeding onesie / lounging suit in silky teal jersey.

• grey fleece inside with teal cotton jersey outside – keeping you cosy & gorgeous throughout your pregnancy and on into breastfeeding

• adjustable tied front gives your tummy more or less room and lets your baby in for skin-to-skin feeding

• no tight waist band around your middle gives you the comfiest way to enjoy your growing body

• eco friendly onesie - our fleece is made from recycled plastic bottles

• available in two sizes w1 & w2

• made in the UK

name: original pink

name: 'bette' mama boe crossover
description:
why not treat yourself or someone you love to perfect comfort at this blossoming time?

• crossover style maternity & breastfeeding onesie in silky teal jersey.

• comfortable and flattering lounging suit in beautiful teal cotton jersey with viscose for stretch. This soft, silky boesuit keeps you comfy and stylish throughout your pregnancy and on into breastfeeding.

• the loose crossover front flatters your tummy and gives you easy access for feeding, while generously cuffed ankles keep your feet free from loose fabric. No tight waist band around your middle gives you the comfiest way to enjoy your growing body.

• available in four sizes m1, m2, m3 & m4

• made in the UK

name: halter polka dot
description:
• halterneck playsuit in soft grey jersey with white polka dots, handmade in the UK.

• this comfortable and flattering playsuit is made in cotton jersey, a silky fabric with 5% lycra for stretch and a beautiful drape.

• the cut is generous around the chest and tummy with leg ties to fit any height. It will fit tall and wide, and is gathered by the belt and leg ties to fit smaller and shorter (model in photo is UK size 10/12 and 5'4" in height.)

• pair with heels for a wedding party or wellies for a festival, this unique handmade suit will make you feel gorgeous and relaxed, the perfect summer outfit.

• one size fits UK 10-18 with or without a belt.

• made in the UK
